'''天主教馬當總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Madangana}}；{{lang-en|Archdiocese of Madang}}）是[[巴布亞紐幾內亞|巴布亞紐幾內亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄四個教區。此總教區是該國四個總教區之一。

==歷史==
1896年2月24日設威廉皇帝地宗座監牧區，1923年11月23日升為東紐幾內亞宗座代牧區，<ref>{{cite journal
|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]
|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社
|date=1923年
|volume=15
|title=''Incumbentis Nobis''
|page=27
|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2015%20%5B1923%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|access-date=2013-06-07
|archive-date=2020-07-13
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713155921/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2015%20%5B1923%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>1966年11月15日升為總教區。<ref>{{cite web |title=NOVAE GUINEAE ORIENTALIS ET INSULARUM ADIACENTIUM |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19661115_novae-guineae.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901083914/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19661115_novae-guineae.html |archivedate=2019-09-01 |language=la |date=1966-11-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==現況==
2004年有教友142,000人（佔轄區總人口49.8%）、廿八個堂區、卅九名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-en|安多尼·巴爾|Anton Bal}}<ref name="Vatican20190726">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 26.07.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/26/190726a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901081044/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/26/190726a.html |archivedate=2019-09-01 |language=en |date=2019-07-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-de|本篤·托-瓦爾平|Benedict To Varpin}}、{{link-de|威廉·庫爾茨 (主教)|Wilhelm Kurtz (Bischof)|威廉·若瑟·庫爾茨}}和{{link-en|斯德望·若瑟·雷切特|Stephen Joseph Reichert}}<ref name="Vatican20190726" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 24.07.2001 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2001/07/24/0421/01231.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901083125/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2001/07/24/0421/01231.html |archivedate=2019-09-01 |language=it |date=2011-07-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 30.11.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/11/30/0745/01710.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901082534/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/11/30/0745/01710.html |archivedate=2019-09-01 |language=it |date=2010-11-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

